Class NonRotamericLibrary.NonRotamericAngles

  • java.lang.Object
    • NonRotamericLibrary.NonRotamericAngles
  • Enclosing class:
    NonRotamericLibrary

    public class NonRotamericLibrary.NonRotamericAngles
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for the probabilistic outcomes. Contains a list of standard torsion angles and a distribution for the last non-rotameric angle. This class is immutable.
